# Zenith

## Your Media. Everywhere.

Stream from your Jellyfin server. Play files from Google Drive. Import your local library.  
One app. All your content.

---

## Play Anything

**4K. Lossless. Free.**

MKV, FLAC, HEVC—Zenith plays your files exactly as they are.  
No quality limits. No subscriptions.

---

## Take It Offline

Download for the road. Access your downloads directly from the Files app.  
Your media, your way.

---

## Never Lose Your Place

Zenith remembers where you left off—across all your devices.

---

## Make It Yours

Edit titles, posters, and descriptions for your local files.  
Your library, your rules.

---

## Zenith Pro

Unlock the full experience.

| Free | Pro |
|------|-----|
| One content type at a time | **All media types together** |
| Switch sources in Settings | **Unified "All Media" tab** |
| Manual metadata editing | **Smart metadata matching** |

**One-time purchase. No subscriptions.**

---

## Built for Every Device

Native Objective-C. Under 5MB.  
Runs beautifully on iOS 11 and later.

*32-bit support (iOS 8+) coming in a future release.*
